### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
### MODERATION — Cola y acciones (ADMIN / MODERATOR)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Get moderation queue (PENDING episodes)
GET {{baseUrl}}/moderation/queue
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get moderation logs (all)
GET {{baseUrl}}/moderation/logs
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get moderation logs for a specific episode
GET {{baseUrl}}/moderation/logs?episodeId={{episodeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ─── Acciones de moderación ───

### Approve episode
POST {{baseUrl}}/moderation/episodes/{{episodeId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Video correcto, corresponde al episodio"
}

### Approve episode with notes
POST {{baseUrl}}/moderation/episodes/{{episodeId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Video correcto",
  "notes": "Calidad 1080p, sin watermarks"
}

### Warn episode
POST {{baseUrl}}/moderation/episodes/{{episodeId}}/warn
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Video no corresponde al episodio",
  "notes": "Minuto 5:15 aparece otro anime"
}

### Disable episode (soft delete)
POST {{baseUrl}}/moderation/episodes/{{episodeId}}/disable
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Contenido inapropiado"
}

### Re-enable episode
POST {{baseUrl}}/moderation/episodes/{{episodeId}}/enable
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Revisado nuevamente, contenido correcto"
}

### ─── Moderación de VideoSources individuales ───

### Disable a single video source (e.g. contenido no relacionado)
POST {{baseUrl}}/moderation/video-sources/{{videoSourceId}}/disable
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Contenido no relacionado al episodio"
}

### Re-enable a video source
POST {{baseUrl}}/moderation/video-sources/{{videoSourceId}}/enable
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Revisado nuevamente, contenido correcto"
}
